text: Blerta Kaqiu (born 24 February 1992) is a Kosovar footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Kosovo women's national team. ==Career== Kaqiu has been capped for the Kosovo national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Kosovan women's footballers Category:Kosovo women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders
